@startuml sq_vcs03_read_diff
' ============================================================
' Title:     VCS-03 — READ Diff
' Boundary:  nasim code agent
' Purpose:   Read diff of staged or unstaged changes
' Milestone: v1.0
' Version:   1.0.0
